59
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:45,790
Only if you love him and he loves you back

60
00:03:45,790 --> 00:03:47,310
can you be together.

61
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:48,990
But if the person you like

62
00:03:48,990 --> 00:03:50,550
