Although the Immortal Clan's soldiers are good,

111
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:28,350
the Demon Clan's soldiers

112
00:06:28,350 --> 00:06:30,080
are also brave and formidable.

113
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:41,750
This

114
