217
00:12:19,990 --> 00:12:21,210
in peace.

218
00:12:21,350 --> 00:12:26,990
Fight! Fight! Fight!

219
00:12:27,310 --> 00:12:28,170
Are you afraid?

220
00:12:28,230 --> 00:12:29,260
No!

221
00:12:29,310 --> 00:12:41,030
Victory! Victory! Victory!

222
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:50,230
